File: Eskom has implemented power cuts. Unsplash/Johannes Plenio JOHANNESBURG - Eskom will implement stage 2 power cuts from 5pm until 10pm on Sunday. It will ramp up to stage 3 from Monday and Tuesday, at the same time. For the rest of the week, you can expect stage 2 from 5pm to 10pm. Since Saturday night, there's been consistent breakdowns at three of South Africa's major power stations. 